Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.28,0:01:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can solve this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.50,0:01:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiraishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.72,0:01:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just called on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.21,0:01:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.38,0:01:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wasn't asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.09,0:02:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot my English textbook!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.71,0:02:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go borrow Kagami's?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They already had English, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.95,0:02:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.14,0:02:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.72,0:02:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should double-check everything the day before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.60,0:02:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa tends to forget stuff a lot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.96,0:02:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.64,0:02:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Konata doesn't forget stuff like textbooks much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I'm surprisingly diligent about those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, I never take my textbook home in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.53,0:02:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not called being diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't review what we went over in class without a textbook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.13,0:02:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never study at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.68,0:02:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you end up cramming the night before...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.68,0:02:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kona-chan's good at putting off stuff till the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That could be why I forget to do my homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.05,0:02:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't forget to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.61,0:02:53.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just don't want to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, show me your homework for Japanese this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Already at it again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.80,0:03:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki's in your class...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask her to show you her homework.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I put this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki-san's such a nice person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that it ends up being hard to ask her for anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this sensation you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get what you're saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.94,0:03:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I still can't accept it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.64,0:03:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.22,0:03:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.17,0:03:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was late because I had to help someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.34,0:03:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I usually go around with this guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.67,0:03:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I just couldn't get away today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.21,0:03:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was like, "It's okay, we can split up..."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.67,0:03:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but the other five of us had gotten one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he was the odd one out...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which kinda left a bad feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.30,0:03:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you've been in the same party for a long time, you wanna help each other out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.48,0:03:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, we all backed him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, friends are a beautiful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.91,0:03:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you were up all night playing online games again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.97,0:03:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kept playing after I logged off, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.65,0:04:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? She's late?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.72,0:04:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.67,0:04:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.39,0:04:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl crashed into me in the shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she suddenly grabbed my hand and took off running.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually, I learned that she'd stolen some taiyaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and was on the run...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what any of this had to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I had no choice but to duck into a café to hide from the taiyaki baker.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:26.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many potential comebacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.45,0:04:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm down with a summer cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.55,0:04:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, I'm terribly sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I need to take a sick day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.70,0:04:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too much gaming again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.38,0:04:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same trick won't work every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.64,0:04:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me guess, you've got a summer cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winter's over and the weather's nice,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:04:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so stop being lazy and get to class!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she totally treated me like the boy who cried wolf yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.72,0:05:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You reap what you sow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.74,0:05:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.05,0:05:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like my fever broke...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.75,0:05:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but my throat still hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means you breathe through your mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.36,0:05:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.69,0:05:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.48,0:05:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can also breathe through your mouth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but wouldn't you usually breathe through your nose?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.94,0:05:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kona-chan breathes through her mouth more than her nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.09,0:05:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a virus enters through your mouth, you get a throat infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.78,0:05:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if a virus enters through your nose, you get a nasal infection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.85,0:05:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, people with sore throats probably had a higher chance of a virus entering through their throat...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.48,0:05:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is when we turn to Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.74,0:05:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.50,0:05:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't feel like doing anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.05,0:06:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About your birthday party today...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about we hold it at my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot that I can't move a step.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.67,0:06:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're baking cookies right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.99,0:06:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.40,0:06:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa and the other one.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.26,0:06:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't abbreviate me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-san and Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.84,0:06:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it isn't much...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I have presents for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.77,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matching earrings!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.94,0:06:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I considered a number of options...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.82,0:06:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I had a hard time making up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.62,0:06:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are presents from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.14,0:06:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, joy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.49,0:06:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brigade chief armband.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.09,0:06:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.25,0:07:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why should I put this on!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.78,0:07:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it would fit you perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll go better on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.11,0:07:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.41,0:07:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Heart!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.91,0:07:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cost a fortune...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wear it with care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to make both of us cosplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's barely any different from our uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.21,0:07:21.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's quite a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's too big...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.11,0:07:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:24.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.20,0:07:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's our birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could hold back a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's cookies are always so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.82,0:07:38.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I baked them with her this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.89,0:07:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kinda learned as I went.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.68,0:07:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having heard that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,some of these cookies don't taste that good anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weird, ain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonder if this is one of Kagami's.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.43,0:07:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well eat the cake, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagamin. Only labors industriously on her birthday. {This sounds weird to me. Re-phrase maybe?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.78,0:07:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zip it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.41,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't there always a fight over how to cut the cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.52,0:08:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you cut a cake into a bunch of slices...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.37,0:08:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...how do you divide up the strawberries on top...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or decide who gets the chocolate decorations?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My older sisters all love chocolate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rats...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.65,0:08:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was off.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't expect that from Kagamin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.28,0:08:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.88,0:08:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.75,0:08:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.42,0:08:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.97,0:08:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My strawberry's awfully small.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.70,0:08:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.97,0:08:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do I have cake on my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.01,0:08:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just discovered another facet of Kagamin's charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound just like Shin-chan, so stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach, the pool, and summer festivals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any other usual events?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.62,0:09:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.12,0:09:08.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summer is all about the annual celebration!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beginning of the battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one and only...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Comiket!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.67,0:09:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That only applies to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.23,0:09:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that like cricket?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.52,0:09:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has their own different thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.33,0:09:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like visiting relatives or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.32,0:09:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, do you have some kind of regular summer activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.19,0:09:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.39,0:09:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be taking a vacation overseas again this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.81,0:09:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.71,0:09:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid bourgeois!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.05,0:09:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that like yogurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.87,0:09:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that you started working at a costume café...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you need a good figure to pull that off?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.92,0:09:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been lamenting my lack of a chest for a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but then this game said...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.88,0:09:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A flat chest is a status symbol!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.70,0:09:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A rarity!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Word for word.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.71,0:10:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when you think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.28,0:10:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a demand, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.76,0:10:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means I'm valuable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know how a line from a game can fill her with confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.25,0:10:12.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I guess I'm okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.26,0:10:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.27,0:10:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a test coming up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you be gaming so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.35,0:10:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would only use some of that passion for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.65,0:10:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your grades would probably go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.15,0:10:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's so easily influenced...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.47,0:10:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't she become a genius if someone released a game that promoted studying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's already stuff like Moe Drill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.18,0:10:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wazzup?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.60,0:10:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a lot of youth crime lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever that happens,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.91,0:10:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the neighbors say:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.70,0:10:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"He was such a nice boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I would never have imagined that he could do such a thing."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.15,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That just means you can't judge a person on the surface. {Missing adjective should replace the second "just"}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.79,0:10:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you ever commit a crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.31,0:11:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always figured she would do something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell the whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.44,0:11:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so hot that I don't feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really understand how you feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you never feel like doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.20,0:11:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making progress on your studying for the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.66,0:11:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was tidying up my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.45,0:11:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how you kinda get the urge to start cleaning when you're feeling the pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know what you mean... {The previous line sounded awkward. She asks whether she "knows" about it, thus, the response shouldn't be "I understand..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.11,0:11:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but study! {Instead of "...but study"}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.87,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.72,0:11:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get a little studying done today!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:11:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a thirty minute break.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.00,0:12:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing my concentration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's already up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just thirty more minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.79,0:12:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Haruhi about to start?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They definitely cut corners with those long-winded Nagato scenes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Ya***** hasn't been very impressive recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.00,0:12:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're already flaming away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not going to happen today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.00,0:12:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go to sleep and wake up early to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.05,0:12:52.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I wake up at five,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can still sleep three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up killing time yesterday by reading manga and watching anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.95,0:13:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like something you would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.74,0:13:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure have some odd taste in manga and games.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You read manga aimed at boys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and mainly play dating sims for men.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad reads manga and plays games a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.43,0:13:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I was probably influenced.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been watching him from the side since I was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand the manga...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but playing dating sims in front of your daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of father is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.71,0:13:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't your mom have anything to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.34,0:13:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...with both of you like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.53,0:13:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.21,0:13:52.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She died when I was really little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'm always doing housework...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.42,0:13:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...which is why I'm way better than Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.66,0:14:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say stuff like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...when the mood isn't right for comebacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.48,0:14:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa's also good at cooking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.66,0:14:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if I would say that I'm good...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.14,0:14:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.93,0:14:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how good Miyuki-san is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.68,0:14:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks rich...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.93,0:14:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so maybe she's bad at housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.24,0:14:17.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cooking, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.09,0:14:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.34,0:14:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only help out from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.13,0:14:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm not very skilled at housework.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.28,0:14:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.77,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.01,0:14:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Miyuki's so good at everything else...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that it doesn't really feel the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.87,0:14:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just assume that she's bad when she says she's bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.94,0:14:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.94,0:14:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what about our teacher?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she lives by herself...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.50,0:14:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but she looks like she could be a slob.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.37,0:14:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These days...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...ya can get by without knowing how ta cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ya got your convenience stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kiddin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.19,0:14:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:15:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About as well as your average person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't make jokes that sound like they're true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa still has my dictionary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, could I get my dictionary back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.79,0:15:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I was doing a little cleaning for a change of pace...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.15,0:15:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.80,0:15:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.68,0:15:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.80,0:15:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people at work are trying to come up with a new menu for summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.97,0:15:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do stuff like that, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.38,0:15:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And wait, did you give up on studying for the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spicy stuff is good when it's hot outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so how about super spicy ramen!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go with something you would usually find in a café.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then a super spicy parfait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.99,0:15:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop skipping the thinking process when you respond?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.38,0:15:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.36,0:16:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why doesn't our school have swimming class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a pool...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.11,0:16:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually relieved by that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.06,0:16:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't open my eyes underwater,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.55,0:16:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't really swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's quite embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are your weaknesses always anything but!? {Unless this is slang, the sentence shouldn't end with "but!?". But what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:26.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The summer Comp Festival is finally about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.94,0:16:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I started working...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.08,0:16:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.72,0:16:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bring so many fond memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you pulling out an ancient reference?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.76,0:16:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the customers start getting excited with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.63,0:16:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...doesn't it feel like everyone's pumped up together for the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.25,0:16:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use some of that passion on academic endeavors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having trouble getting to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.53,0:17:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll read until I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.26,0:17:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I happen to have some stuff I just bought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.41,0:17:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So much for falling asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.85,0:17:18.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.86,0:17:20.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm feeling really sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.48,0:17:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand turning off your phones around priority seats...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of pacemakers and the like.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.46,0:17:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do they ban cell phone use for the whole train?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.48,0:17:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.43,0:17:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll disturb other people when you talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.70,0:17:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.87,0:17:47.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't trains already noisy with people talking anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.85,0:17:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That includes men and women of all ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.61,0:17:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to work at the temple for summer festivals like for New Year's Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.19,0:17:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.11,0:18:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't work in the summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.95,0:18:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting to that time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.26,0:18:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you on a diet?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.42,0:18:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's because of all the studying...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I weighed myself yesterday, it was down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.22,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I figured it'd be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.74,0:18:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And like, you're weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.20,0:18:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.06,0:18:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kona-chan, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.09,0:18:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Kagami?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.55,0:18:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Konata!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.77,0:18:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My weight already...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...went all the way up in like the blink of an eye...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's 'cause you let go and started snacking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And wasn't that a senryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.83,0:18:37.34,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,[Senryu is a Japanese form of short poetry similar to haiku in construction.]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only ate a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:48.72,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like a kilo or two more or less is going to affect how you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.72,0:18:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you get so excited and depressed over every kilogram?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is why women are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.13,0:18:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you supposed to be a woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to another episode of Lucky Channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.85,0:19:12.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has everyone been doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kogami Akira, always running at 120%!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.07,0:19:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nyoron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the assistant, Shiraishi Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interrupt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.90,0:19:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a kiddy ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Learn the job already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to be dropped from this role?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it my all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.94,0:19:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have big news for everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.26,0:19:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Published in the November issue of Comptiq...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Project Fashionable Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.09,0:19:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already received this many postcards from everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.96,0:19:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.84,0:19:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think there was another person involved in that project...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for all the feedback!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like cowabunga!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think anyone's going to understand a joke from the eighties...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:12.02,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll reveal the idea I've selected after extensive review.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.85,0:20:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.60,0:20:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from a Miss Chery in Satte, Saitama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Project Fashionable Akira!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kagami-san's twin tails look great on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.78,0:20:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if Akira-san also wore twin tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,twin tails, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:31.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair styling is a woman's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I split it in two...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it might look lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.72,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No ifs or buts about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it impossible with your hair length...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.23,0:20:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like long hair is always a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.82,0:20:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akira-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.44,0:20:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It weighs a lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.92,0:20:50.09,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really gonna show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:51.57,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Like if you just twitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain to maintain.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.05,0:20:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And frankly, it isn't in fashion right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys run their mouth off about liking long hair on women...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.53,0:21:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but do they have any idea how much time, effort and money it takes to maintain?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:21:01.14,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking about yourself now.{not sure where this goes}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.14,0:21:03.57,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not in character anymore. {In character or an character? Re-confirmation needed.}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:04.65,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no longer Akira-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.56,0:21:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And nobody ever notices your efforts...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.65,0:21:05.54,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.07,Default-Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.07,0:21:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As for what Akira would look like with twin tails...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.40,0:21:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can find out more on our homepage or the radio show!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.34,0:21:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope to see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.88,0:21:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both hands will be waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.16,0:21:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then please look forward to next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.17,0:21:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was with the attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By attitude, you mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you keep cutting in?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That upset about getting burned in the beginning? {Sounds weird. Please consult TL/TLC about this line}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.42,0:21:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.29,0:21:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I just figured nobody would recognize cowabunga now...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.51,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we start over again?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.40,0:21:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:42.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard they're holding an audition for Shiraishi Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.22,0:21:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.28,0:21:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first I've heard about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.08,0:21:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can try out if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try out? Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.69,0:21:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm actually him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.23,0:21:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:57.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're amazing, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sing anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as it's an anime song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.65,0:22:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can sing well in many different voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.43,0:22:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Singing anime songs is all about staying true to the original song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.65,0:22:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.98,0:22:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you gonna sing, Onee-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.77,0:22:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The title was displayed earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.73,0:22:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I didn't recognize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:21.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miyuki, you don't know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.24,0:22:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you aren't any better.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.72,0:22:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard this before!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.62,0:22:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you watching the series with me a while ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.58,0:22:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.67,0:22:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still prefer the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.91,0:22:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an old geezer or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.35,0:22:47.71,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,You're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:51.54,Default-Left,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is the \Nbest singer out of us sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.33,0:23:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Week was apparently derived from industry lingo for the period when movie ticket sales are extremely high.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.31,0:23:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: Ace Shooter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.16,0:23:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to next time!
